joelib2.feature
Interface NativeValue

All Known Implementing Classes:
APropDoubleResult, APropIntResult, BooleanResult, DoubleResult, IntResult
public interface NativeValue

Interface to have a fast method to getting native descriptor values. This is a better method than checking class names and forces the developer to implement fast accesing methods without class casting methods.
